meta.description: Libassuan  is the IPC library used by some GnuPG related software
meta.name: libassuan

meta.description: Libassuan, the IPC library used by GnuPG and related software
meta.long_description:
Libassuan is a small library implementing the so-called Assuan
protocol.  This protocol is used for IPC between most newer
GnuPG components.  Both, server and client side functions are
provided.
meta.name: libassuan
